  <description>PDK Red Series Power-over-Ethernet daughtercard. Its footprint and the relative locations of the six-pin PoE Out and four-pin PoE In headers are calibrated from the manufacturer Red 2 installation graphic. Electrical assignments remain generic pending a verified factory pinout.</description>
